OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe evening
OL,6,Fwill start largely sunny. However, a
OL,7,Ffew heavy and possibly thundery
OL,8,Fshowers could break out towards dusk,
OL,9,Fand areas of cloud are likely to bring
OL,10,Ffurther showers across the region from
OL,11,Fthe south overnight. Very mild, though
OL,12,Fbreezy.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FEarly showers will die out
OL,15,Ffrom the south in the morning, leaving
OL,16,Fa dry day with a southerly breeze and
OL,17,Fplenty of very warm or hot sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
