OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FWarm
OL,6,Fsunshine and a few showers on Friday.
OL,7,FTurning cooler and more unsettled over
OL,8,Fthe weekend, with some showery and
OL,9,Fbreezy weather arriving from the west.
